    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-cared for over the years. The exterior is overall very presentable, though it shows some minor signs of regular use such as small stone chips on the hood and light scratches near the door handles. Inside, the cabin remains clean and comfortable, with only slight wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car is sound, starts reliably, and has a consistent service history. It offers a great balance of reliability and value for its next owner.",
